title: Superpowers
description:
Superpowers, written by Caitlin Tegart. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, May 19, 2008.

Starring Scott Courlander, D'Arcy Erokan, Fran Gillespie, Nate Lang, and Joe Spellman. Directed by Neil W. Casey.
